UMW                   
    PC357 
R
SOP4, DC Input Photo Transistor Coupler
Description
The UMW PC357 series combine an AlGaAs 
infrared emitting diode as the emitter which is 
optically coupled to a silicon planar phototran
sistor detector in a plastic SOP4 package.
With the robust coplanar double mold structure, 
UMW PC357 series provide the most stable 
isola-tion feature.
